msgid ""
":doc:`Mesh snapping </editors/3dview/object/transform/transform_control/"
"precision/snap>` also works with curve components. Both control points and "
"their handles will be affected by snapping, except for within itself (other "
"components of the active curve). Snapping works with 2D curves but points "
"will be constrained to the local XY axes."
msgstr ""
"Le :doc:`Mesh snapping </editors/3dview/object/transform/transform_control/"
"precision/snap>` fonctionne aussi avec ui-même (autres composants de la "
"courbe active). Snapping* fonctionne avec les courbes 2D mais les points "
"seront restreints aux axes locaux XY. "

